        <title>Protecting Workers and Improving Labor Standards Act</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To repeal the authority under the National Labor Relations Act for States to enact laws prohibiting agreements requiring membership in a labor organization as a condition of employment, and for other purposes.</title>
      </item>
